ull test suite were observed but are unrelated to this task and documented in ESCALATIONS.md).\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe derivation logic and tests are well-implemented. The backward compatibility with legacy aliases in `SamplePlay` and `JournalEntry` remains intact.\n"}}
